-- Pfizer Faces Menopause Drug Trials as Judge Sends 200 Cases to Home Courts
-- Jef Feeley
-- 2010-06-18T14:58:42Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-18/pfizer-faces-menopause-drug-trials-as-judge-sends-200-cases-to-home-courts.html

          
          
             Pfizer Inc. faces a trial in Texas
over its hormone-replacement drug Prempro after a judge
overseeing litigation over the medicines sent 200 cases back to
their home courts.  
